===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro}} {{term|lang=fro|ableté}} (French {{term|lang=fr|habileté}}, earlier spelling {{term|lang=fr|habilité}} with [[silent]] ''h''), from {{etyl|la}} {{term|lang=la|habilitas||[[aptitude]], ability}}, from {{term|lang=la|habilis||apt, able}} apparently.  See [[able]].

